(1974,	'_transient_villatheme_item_5455',	'a:6:{s:4:\"code\";i:300;s:4:\"name\";s:54:\"CURCY - WooCommerce Multi Currency - Currency Switcher\";s:3:\"url\";s:53:\"https://villatheme.com/extensions/woo-multi-currency/\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"2.3.8\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:24602:\"/**2.3.8 - 2025.04.11**/\r\n- Update: Add new sidebar layout\r\n- Update: Add display name color for new layout\r\n- Update: Add top position setting for sidebar\r\n- Update: Add Openexchangerates, Exchagerate API, Currencyapi Finance API\r\n- Fix: Conflict with Learnpress and some addons of Learnpress\r\n\r\n/**2.3.7 - 2025.02.28**/\r\n- Update: Add filter \'wmc_previous_currency_cart_item_price\' to format cart item price\r\n- Update: Add compatible code with GIFT4U  Gift Cards All in One for Woo\r\n- Update: Add setting description\r\n- Update: Change ajax reload filter price code flow\r\n- Fix: Conflict with WooCommerce Subscriptions\r\n\r\n/**2.3.6 - 2024.12.21**/\r\n- Fix: Conflict with WooCommerce Wholesale Prices Premium\r\n- Fix: Conflict with WooCommerce Extra Product Options by ThemeHigh\r\n- Update: Add setting to switch currency when user login\r\n\r\n/**2.3.5 - 2024.10.28**/\r\n- Fix: Finance API XE return wrong data\r\n- Update: Add setting to change currency switcher layout\r\n- Update: Add setting to change currency switcher color, background\r\n- Update: Add setting to display product price collate in multiple currencies\r\n\r\n/**2.3.4 - 2024.09.27**/\r\n- Fix: Price issues with Wpfunnels\r\n- Fix: Loading icon when update currency rate\r\n- Fix: Currency symbol when filter price\r\n- Fix: Compatible cache plugin by json when loading wc ajax\r\n- Update: Add some setting description\r\n\r\n/**2.3.3 - 2024.07.12**/\r\n- Fix: Checkout issues when only one currency active\r\n- Fix: Price issues with WPFunnels\r\n- Fix: Price issues with WC Fields Factory\r\n- Fix: Filter price issues with cache\r\n\r\n/**2.3.2 - 2024.01.26**/\r\n- Fix: Conflict with WooCommerce Amazon Pay\r\n- F