(239,	1,	'2025-06-03 05:23:28',	'2025-06-03 05:23:28',	'<b>Last Updated: March 2025</b>\nAt [site name], we take pride in delivering high-quality digital products and ensuring a seamless customer experience. We understand that issues may sometimes arise with digital downloads, and we strive to provide fair solutions. This policy outlines the circumstances under which virtual and digital file products may be granted refunds, replacements, or store credits.\n<ul>\n 	<li><b>Eligibility for Returns &amp; Refunds</b></li>\n</ul>\nSince digital products are intangible and cannot be physically returned, our refund policy is structured to ensure fairness while preventing misuse. You may be eligible for a refund under the following circumstances:\n1.1 Defective, Corrupted, or Inaccessible FilesIf the digital file you receive is:\nCorrupt or Unusable (e.g., the file does not open, has missing components, or displays errors),Incomplete (e.g., missing key elements advertised in the product description), orinaccessible due to technical issues. You must report the problem within 7 days of purchase. We will attempt to provide a corrected file, and if a working file cannot be provided, a full refund will be issued.\n<b>1.2 Duplicate Purchases</b>\nIf you accidentally purchase the same digital product more than once, you are eligible for a refund of the duplicate charge. However, refunds for choosing the wrong one will not be issued if multiple product variations are available (e.g., different licensing options).\n<b>1.3 Incorrect Product Delivered</b>\nIf you receive the wrong digital product due to a system error or misdelivery, please get in touch with us within 7 days of purchase. We will provide the correct product or offer a refund if the item is unavailable.\n<b>1.4 Unauthorized Charges or Fraudulent Transactions</b>\nIf you notice an unauthorized charge related to our digital products on your account, please report it immediately. After verifying the claim, we will issue a refund for the unauthorized purchase.\n<ul>\n 	<li><b>Non-Refundable Situations</b></li>\n</ul>\nIn certain situations, refunds will not be granted due to the nature of digital products. These include:\n<b>2.1 Change of Mind</b>\nWe do not provide refunds if you change your mind after purchasing. Please review the product description, compatibility, and features before purchasing.\n<b>2.2 Software or Compatibility Issues</b>\nBefore purchasing, the customer must ensure the digital product is compatible with their system, software, or device.\nWe do not offer refunds if the product does not work due to incompatibility with third-party software or outdated system requirements.\n<b>2.3 User Error or Accidental Download Deletion</b>\nIf you accidentally delete the downloaded file, we will provide a new download link, but we will not issue a refund.\n<b>2.4 Unauthorized Sharing or Policy Violations</b>\nIf we detect that a digital product has been shared, distributed, resold, or misused, the refund request will be denied, and further actions may be taken.\n<b>2.5 Subscription-Based or Licensed Digital Products</b>\nDigital products that are part of a subscription, membership, or licensed content may not be eligible for refunds.\n<ul>\n 	<li><b>Refund Process</b></li>\n</ul>\nIf you are eligible for a refund, follow these steps to initiate the process:\n<b>Step 1: Contact Customer Support</b>\nSend an email to [site email] with:\nYour Order Number\nThe Product Name\nA Description of the Issue\nScreenshots or Proof of the problem (if applicable)\n<b>Step 2: Review &amp; Approval</b>\nOur team will review your request within 2-5 business days.\nIf approved, you will receive a confirmation email and refund details.\nIf denied, we will explain the decision.\n<b>Step 3: Refund Issuance</b>\nOnce approved, refunds will be processed via the original payment method within five business days.\nRefunds typically reflect within 5-10 business days, depending on your payment provider.\